title: When in Elo Hell and you ask someone to play more safely so they don't feed

replies.body: That is because saying "dont feed" is actually not useful information OR helpful.
it should be when you're running in one v five. what it means is STOP BEING FUCKING RETARDED, WE WOULD RATHER YOU AFKED IF YOU DONT STOP. AFK IS A BETTER TEAMMATE THAN YOU.
LOL I crei when I'm jungling and top dies twice and then wastes all forms of disengage on engaging the enemy and then they die and go "shitty jungler no ganks" like..... pls....
Well, at that point the lane opponent is probably fed enough to tower-dive and survive.
